Interface QueryableDataSource

All Superinterfaces:
DataSource
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractSource, BulkDataSource, BundlesSource, CatalogSource, DatasetSource, DeltaSource, FileSource, NdjsonSource, ParquetSource
public interface QueryableDataSource extends DataSource
A FHIR data source that can be queried, and can also be written out to a data sink.
